Do you despise lonely nights? Do you hate when you have to Netflix and chill... by yourself? Are you loathing the approach of Valentines Day?

We've got just the thing! Single Ladies and Eligible Bachelors for the taking! Come in and meet these purr filled, fluffy, and quite adorable single felines!
A relaxed introduction in our cat room starts your date off right. Did he just make biscuits while looking deep into your eyes? Did she purr so hard she drooled? If you think it's love, you can take this date to the next level and bring your new-found feline companion home!

AVAILABLE FOR ADOPTION!!! Meet Patches an adorable 1-2 year old Lab/Terrier mix. Patches has an incredibly sweet disposition. She is an easy going girl that loves everyone she meet. Patches was recently rescued from an area shelter and is adjusting wonderfully in her foster home. She is very smart girl that is very eager to please. She already knows commands like sit, stay and lay down. She is good on the leash and is a joy to walk. She is house and crate trained. If you looking for a new addition to your family or just a loyal companion look no further Patches is the girl for you. She is spayed, current on vaccines and microchipped. She currently weighs 45lbs and is full grown. Patches is ready and waiting to meet her forever family.
